{"tid":585920,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"講真，港獨無出路","createTime":"2018-03-09T05:56:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-21T07:12:56.000Z","uid":26332,"like":57,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c85d8f08fc9b32f481d235e6482176d5031f500d","tid":585920,"uid":26332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T05:56:28.000Z","msg":"唯一出路係一國一制<br />\n實行高度自治，港人治國<br />\n自古以來，中國係屬於香港<br />\n首都應該遷往香港<br />\n奉行林鄭新時代香港特色資本主義制度思想，並貫徹科學園發展觀<br />\n原有行政長官升格為大總統，並不設連任限制<br />\n咁就大家都happy啦，你話好唔好呀？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27edd8d9431ee36b99c0a6b7c45f9a61273bfe0e","tid":585920,"uid":26332,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T06:03:21.000Z","msg":"遷都後實行種族分離政策，防止北方蠻橫南下，必要時局部地區宵禁<br />\n統一講廣東話，方言得以保留(除左普通話)<br />\n廢除簡體字<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"115793ee290e6f96f601d0e592b8792c8678adca","tid":585920,"uid":26332,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T06:07:19.000Z","msg":"進入首都香港必須通過檢查，絕對有權篩選低等人口防止污染首都<br />\n強制前朝國人再接受教育，洗脫共産黨思維<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b17b00b717bdd236a632b8bb3fc8d9163773e316","tid":585920,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T06:07:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1aaa0f71f93692cb52916a5a2ffa1b05e21a8397","tid":585920,"uid":26332,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"b17b00b717bdd236a632b8bb3fc8d9163773e316","tid":585920,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T06:07:33.